ults. For these\nmolecules, the values of the dielectric constant and the surface tension\npresent errors of the order of 10% with the experimental data. Miscibility of\nthe amines was also tested with the new parameters and the results show\nreasonable agreement with experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 12:08:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
