omising candidates for\nnovel functional materials, which will provide a broad prospect for the\nrealization of ultrathin ferroelectric devices in optoelectronics due to their\nspontaneous polarization characteristics and high Curie temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 13:08:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
