 are strongly normalising.\nThis is an extension (and small simplification) of Gandy's proof for the\nlambda-calculus, which additionally emphasizes its latent operational\nintuition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 14:01:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
