f the literature, we expect the string\nlandscape to favor EW natural SUSY models over finetuned models so that the\nlandscape is not an alternative to naturalness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 14:56:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
